{"tid":1521490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經過呢場運動，我真係好愛香港人。","createTime":"2019-08-31T08:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T08:45:53.000Z","uid":172443,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e330ec2d2c01c8d4e6bf8d04c85361193c7f8d87","tid":1521490,"uid":172443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"每次出嚟 無論係文宣定勇武 你地都會成日走嚟問我洗唔洗幫手塞野比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼街招 拎走我d文宣 強行幫我貼 希望快啲貼完我唔好比人打 <br />\n<br />\n派傳單 個個都同我講 唔洗啦 加油 聽日見 再唔係就次次都有和理非係到叫停我同我傾成粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n機場 好撚柒多物資 見你地十幾二十架車推嚟推去 塞我地食野 重要糖水都有 好多公公婆婆捉實我地叫我地小心但個日我地只係行行企企叫口號 明明你地仲辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有手足想做傻事 你地成班痴線佬又即刻沖落街揾人<br />\n<br />\n勇武更加唔洗講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最辛苦嘅永遠唔係累、無力嘅時候，係我每次聽到有人抹黑，話我地叫左錢、暴徒，我都好撚嬲，請問要收幾多錢先可以令一個人咁撚正直善良？<br />\n請問邊撚到嘅暴徒會係用條命去爭取公義，係會用晒戶口嘅錢去幫人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個月前，我好憎香港，一早就plan左會讀master移民，因為香港真係好壓迫好冷漠。<br />\n但點會點會估到，三個月後嘅我會體驗到咁撚多野。<br />\n<br />\n真係好愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚一個都唔可以少！！！"},{"pid":"bc5b32b87daacdb18559b34b1504fb1a70897578","tid":1521490,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=208a96e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=498ac34c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=be8a2e89\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"16401cc99c8356280b229e0527b51efab95bfc72","tid":1521490,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"前線係你相像不到恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02f0083d999fa398b4e3c2f44f183550e7c21a8","tid":1521490,"uid":162910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"exactly the same<br />\n未試過咁有歸屬感<br />\n民族自決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb09707b8cb802fd0029bff80e82f3857ad0dba","tid":1521490,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還我真普選！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日港島見！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Sogo&mdash;&mdash;&gt;遮打<br />\n遮打&mdash;&mdash;&gt;Sogo</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3793b25ab422c7beab21c19a3d3578bd273b6b62","tid":1521490,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01582145098f57686c966a26c0ab59348dd89b94","tid":1521490,"uid":162910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3793b25ab422c7beab21c19a3d3578bd273b6b62","tid":1521490,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0